  <a href="https://bmcvetres.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/s12917-016-0633-8" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-describedby="a11y-external-message">https://bmcvetres.biomedcentral.com</a><br></span><span style="text-decoration-line: underline;"><br>
  
